  "title": "Mechanical Engineering Technician",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $2800 - $3500 + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Tuas / On-site</strong></li><li><strong>Working days:</strong> <strong>Monday to Friday (8am to 5pm), Saturday (8am to 12pm)</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Service, repair, install, load testing on crane and hoists system</strong></li><li><strong>Assist in the setup and commissioning of overhead cranes, hoists, and related mechanical systems</strong></li><li><strong>Conduct routine maintenance and servicing of mechanical equipment to ensure optimal performance</strong></li><li>Diagnose mechanical issues and perform necessary repairs to minimize downtime</li><li>Any ad hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Possess minimum GCE O level with minimum 1-2 years of relevant experience</li><li>Possess electrical knowledge/experience</li><li><strong>Possess with Singapore driving license </strong></li><li><strong>Training provided for those without/lesser experience</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
